Subject: Re: SQLDirectory
References: <DNEDJIGLNAJOFEMFBJIJOEPACDAA.plaflamme@konova.com>
In-Reply-To: <DNEDJIGLNAJOFEMFBJIJOEPACDAA.plaflamme@konova.com>
