        </pre>
      </blockquote>
    </blockquote>
    <pre wrap="">and 
    </pre>
    <blockquote type="cite">
      <blockquote type="cite">
        <pre wrap="">stemming?

Using term frequencies of the document is not really possible
        </pre>
      </blockquote>
    </blockquote>
    <pre wrap="">since 
    </pre>
    <blockquote type="cite">
      <blockquote type="cite">
        <pre wrap="">lucene
is not providing access to a document vector, isn't it?
        </pre>
      </blockquote>
